archived.name: Design-and-implementation-of-Antenna
archived.description: This project provides a simple and well-documented MATLAB implementation of a Phase-Locked Loop (PLL), developed as part of a 5th semester mini project. The final version focuses on clarity, structure, and ease of understanding.

archived.name: GenAI
archived.description: Explore AI-assisted games and projects, created and refined during the 5th semester of university. From unbeatable Tic-Tac-Toe to maze adventures, enjoy fun and challenging experiences!

archived.name: url-redir
archived.description: This repository provides a customizable URL redirector hosted on GitHub Pages. It redirects users based on URL fragments, with options for a confirmation popup and bulk URL handling. The rules are defined in a JSON file, and the project features a responsive, dark-themed UI with toast notifications.
